Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.37,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}In this room filled with light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.92,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I'll be waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:28.61,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}If you'd realize you're floating and gazing upon a box,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:33.74,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You'd notice it doesn't return your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:40.37,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The reflected heart is pure white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:46.50,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Just like the light from the falling snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:51.92,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}This shivering rain that blankets me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:58.84,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Isn't going to dispel until the spring breeze returns
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.31,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}So let's search for some azalea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:06.48,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Bring me with you to a comforting garden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.52,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Is not something I can ask
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:16.69,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}That fairy tale-like happiness isn't real
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.57,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I know that much already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.37,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}But still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:25.83,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to go there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:27.08,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Laughter resounds in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.63,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And then it can't be heard anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:45.81,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I'd rather not force myself to laugh and try to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:53.92,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I'd rather drown and freeze it in silence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.94,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I don't mind getting hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:06.61,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Before the setting sun disappears beyond the ocean's horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:12.21,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}If I could tell you it was all a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:22.83,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Maybe we could get back to our shining days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:28.48,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Just the two of us alone again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:34.54,Yahari ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Hello! Hello! Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}U-Um, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Things like flexible work hours exist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:10.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As someone aiming to become part of the elite, I'd like from now on—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.11,Yahai main alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought you wanted to be a stay-at-home husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I believe you said that to work was to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:19.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's just that it's wrong to label lateness as evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:21.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll hear what you have to say before I hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The police start moving after an incident occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:27.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,and it's common knowledge that the hero always arrives late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:30.29,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But do you still condemn the hero for being late?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Paradoxically, I'd say lateness is justic—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Hitting is not—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.35,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There are so many problem children in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Flexible hours for you as well, Kawasaki Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Black lace?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.26,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I guess it's Yukinon's turn to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then we'll start with Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Finish the following idiom, "If a butterfly flaps its wings..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.61,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Tokyo-Chiba train line will stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is this some kind of quiz about Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:08.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yuigahama, recently they keep it going at reduced speeds actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The answer is, "It might cause a hurricane somewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Next question relates to geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What are Chiba's two local specialties?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Miso peas and boiled peas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Do you think all Chiba has is peas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Oh, it's just Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I thought some creeper was randomly talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So you were also invited to the study group, Hachiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What's with that look as if someone you didn't invite just showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We didn't invite you to the study group, so what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Quit saying such spiteful things as if you were simply stating facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.85,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Documents for summer courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:46.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're already studying for exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:50.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Haven't most people aiming for college already started?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm aiming for a prep school scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Scrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:04:00.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Prep schools these days give tuition breaks for students with good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:05.16,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if I get tuition from my parents, all that money will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's swindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.26,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,His ill nature is at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's fine if no one's disadvantaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.63,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brother?{i hate using this, but meh}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Komachi? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,My friend here asked me for some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hikigaya Komachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always being kind to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm his classmate, Totsuka Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well aren't you cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There you go, joking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.34,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:41.34,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya. I'm Hikki's classmate, Yuigahama Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.98,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Yukinoshita Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:05:00.85,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm not really his classmate or his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Quite regrettably, his acquaintance, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,"Regrettably?" And a question, even?{editor: he's basically asking why she phrased the regret as a question}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm Kawasaki Taishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm in the same cram school as Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,My sister is a second year at Sobu High too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.81,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Her name is Kawasaki Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Black lace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kawasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's a bit scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Isn't she a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, I've talked to her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But don't ask a girl stuff like that. It's hard to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:39.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I've seen her get along with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I heard that Taishi's older sister turned into a delinquent recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She even comes home late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:49.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So he asked me how to get her to become her old self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.85,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,About when did this all start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ever since she started going to Sobu High.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.46,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She was really diligent in middle school, and kind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,In other words, she changed after joining the same class as Hikigaya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.98,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to say it like it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Am I some kind of virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I didn't say you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Isn't your imagination just running wild, Hikigerma?{yeah, not sure how to express this joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You said it. You definitely said germ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.85,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I{ just} stuttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:18.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's Hikigaya germs! Touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I had a barrier up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Barriers aren't effective against Hikigaya germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,"Barriers aren't effective"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How freaking strong are Hikigaya germs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:30.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So like, what time does she come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I get home pretty late too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,After 5 AM or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that more like morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Don't your parents say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,They both work, and we have a younger brother and sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so they don't really fuss about her that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Familial circumstances, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.43,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:53.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.91,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Taishi is the younger brother of Kawasaki Saki, a student at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Considering that he asked for advice about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I think this falls under the Volunteers Club's jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,but it would be best for her to solve the problem herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,rather than us solving it for her.{timing might need to be adjusted for line lengths?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.35,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So what exactly did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Do you know about animal therapy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do with my cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:33.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,By letting her play with the cat, we'll draw out the kindness in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:36.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely pick it up{the cat} if she's moved by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's not some old-school delinquent leader, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I've decided on everyone's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Everyone get into position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.34,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:04.81,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, you were just talking to my cat, Kamakura.{this his name? 今 ウチのカマクラに話しかけて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I believe you were ordered to be on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Can't you even do something so simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.91,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I had assumed your mental capabilities to be low,{あなたの\N程度の低さは計算に入れてたけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,but I honestly didn't think they were this low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If I say anything more, she'll kill me. It's in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:23.57,Yahai main alt,,0,0,0,,Even grade schoolers can do what you tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What's up, Komachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:31.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brother? It's Taishi. I just heard from Hikigaya—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't have the right to call me Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why'd you hang up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Waiting for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.21,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,My sister is allergic to cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's true that there are things you just can't talk about with your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:54.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,but couldn't you talk to other adults instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I hear you've been going home late recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Who'd you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I can't divulge the identity of my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.36,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Regardless, answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Does it really matter where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm causing anyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You might later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you considered your parents' feelings at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:33.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's no way you could have experience with things such as a parent's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Being single and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.46,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You should really worry about your own future instead of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Like marriage, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, someone marry{accept, receive, etc} her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If she changed for the worse, how about trying to change her one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely go better this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And how can we change her, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's only one reason a girl will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Afternoon. You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Is it 'cause of a part time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Everything in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to act so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't need your consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It seems like I was rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's mean to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's cool. I'm not worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:41.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm not your Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:48.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it looks like Taishi's sister got a phone call from some weird shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:55.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She got a phone call from the shop manager of some Angel something or another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.36,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After doing a little searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.11,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I found out that it's a shop called Angel in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are only two shops that stay open until early morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And this place here is one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know that much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What kind of shop is a maid café?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:15.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't really know either, so I called someone who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{is he saying something? cc have おっほんむ！ but idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So it's finally my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that face when you were the ones who called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.21,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I just thought responding would be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then be silent and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Let's go have the maids pamper us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Pamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't this place for guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What would we do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It looks like girls are welcome too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master. Woof.{i reallly have no idea how to make this sound like a dog}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.36,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:03.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you look so cute, Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Right, Hachiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hmph. You're merely cosplaying a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no heart in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.08,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Yukinon, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:24.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You look great! So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it seems like Kawasaki isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.43,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Did you check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Her name wasn't on the shift schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:37.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,They called her home, so if you think about it, it's unlikely she used an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.63,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Quite strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A haughty girl is working secretly.{feel free to localize tsuntsun, i just don't feel like thinking about it atm}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,"Meow, meow. Welcome home, Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,"Wait! What are you doing here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:51.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That was fated to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We're going to the second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.26,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,On the top floor of Hotel Royal Okura,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:01.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,is Angel's Ladder, the stairway to heaven.{since he translates it to jp}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,They don't have any clothes to get past the dress code requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Still, these clothes came from Yukinon's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's got a ton just like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She even lives alone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, who are you, Yukinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I have them only because I sometimes get the chance to dress like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Normally, people don't get such chances, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Quit glancing around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Straighten up, and stick your chest out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Lower your chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Who might you be again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:00.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're in the same class, yet she doesn't remember you. Forgettable as always, Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So he's from Sobu High too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:08.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't for a date or anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:19.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you looked at this thing next to me? The mere suggestion is insulting.{lit. saying that having seen this thing next to me is of questionable taste even if intended as a joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:24.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I get that you're bickering with her, but could you not poke fun at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I hear you're going home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Your little brother is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:34.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So it's your fault everyone around me is being so fussy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:38.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Taishi said to you guys, but don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:43.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Cinderella's magic is broken at midnight,{ｼﾝﾃﾞﾚﾗの魔法が解けるのは 午前０時だけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.61,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so yours will be broken here.{あなたの魔法は ここで解けるわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:52.45,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Once the magic is broken, won't the happy end be waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it will, Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.46,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I think you ought to watch out for the bad end, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are these two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We aren't supposed to work late at night at our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:08.59,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,In other words, Yukinoshita is suggesting that Kawasaki is falsifying her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I see. Why don't they just say that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any intention to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:20.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I also work part time whenever I don't have any money,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,but I've never lied about my age to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.98,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I just need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:31.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How can someone who thinks working is losing understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So you heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're underestimating life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm not working because I want money to fool around or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me in with that fool over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You guys talk big, but can you provide money for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Are you guys going to shoulder the costs that my parents couldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Any further barking—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:56.98,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't your father a member of the Diet prefectural assembly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no way someone who lives so comfortably would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Yukinon's family has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then mine doesn't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:14.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true, but Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I just knocked my glass over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I've got to talk to you about Taishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hear me out tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Five thirty at the WcD's on main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what it's about then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:34.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,This isn't enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She didn't pay for mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Taishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, being out this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:51.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing, being out until so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki, why is it you're working?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why did you need the money? Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Taishi, has anything changed since you entered your third year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I started going to a cram school, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I get it. It's to pay for his tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,He's been attending cram school since April.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:19.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That means that the problem of his tuition is already sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:24.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The little brother isn't the only one who needs tuition paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Our school is for college-bound students,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:29.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so most people are consciously preparing for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,They begin seriously thinking about summer classes and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:39.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's why I said it's fine if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I plan to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to bother you or our parents about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Um, can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:53.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, both our parents work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:57.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I hated it when I came home to an empty house,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:02.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't my parents who came for me, but my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:06.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, he started coming home before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I really feel grateful towards him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:13.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he coming home early because he had no friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,From Yukipedia or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:22.91,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I totally agree, but my version made me sound smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to say with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Just as how you don't want to be a bother to your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:33.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Taishi doesn't want to be a bother to you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If only you'd understand that, the younger sibling would then be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki, do you know about scholarships?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Are all siblings like that, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it depend on the person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You could also say they're the closest stranger to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.16,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's something I understand quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You actually did end up meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:13.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You know, the sweets person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that little bit of pain, you got to meet someone as cute as Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What did she just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama is the sweets person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The owner of the dog I saved on the day of the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Want to buy bread on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:33.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's all, and that ends the workplace field trip. Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What took you? Everyone's already left for the family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.52,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad leaving you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You really are kind, Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence that I saved your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:22.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'd probably still be alone even if the accident never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no reason at all for you to fret over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You really didn't have to mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to worry about me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If you're being kind because you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,then stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder why it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not really like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:54.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The ever kind Yuigahama will probably be kind to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:12.08,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I hate those types of kind girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You can't get them off your mind if they merely say hi to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Just a single text from them can make your heart flutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:23.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then if you get a call from them, you'll just keep happily looking at the call history like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But I know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,About that thing called "kindness."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:32.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If someone is kind to me, they're also kind to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I almost forget that sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If the truth is that cruel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.59,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,then I'm sure lies are truly kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's why kindness is a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:48.21,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I always get my hopes up and end up misunderstanding every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,At some point I just gave up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:55.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm an experienced loner. I'll never again fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm a veteran warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm the absolute best at losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:06.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So I will forever hate kind girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.72,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H313A3B&\fs60\pos(700.8,188.4)\b1\blur0.5}He once again returns the way he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Darn, and here I had some expectations for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not like Yuigahama has quit—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:46.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't come, it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:51.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what sort of things she liked, or what her hobbies were.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:55.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I guess I got a bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:58.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I want to talk this through with you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.23,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to trouble yourself with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So that's why it's over with this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:04.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:10.03,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2C3032&\fs60\b1\blur0.5\pos(620.8,186.8)}At last, his and her beginning will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:06.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,At last, his and her beginning will come to an end.
